
;傭兵アルバイトに奴隷を捕まえてきてもらう
@MILESTONE_CHECK_810

SIF GETBIT(＃マイルストーン達成／奴隷捕獲＃)
	RETURN 1


;施設【町役場】解放・＜魔力枷＞2コ入手
@MILESTONE_REWARD_810

ITEM:魔力枷 += 2
PRINTL A mercenary part-timer has delivered a captured slave. You'll train her to be a fine 「Dairy Cow」.
PRINTL From now on, it seems that if you ask them to capture humans found on Makai,
PRINTL they will do so just like they did this time.
PRINTL You didn't notice before he mentioned it, but the the Makai newspaper
PRINTL had a small column titled "Ningen information confirmed today."
PRINTL However, he adds that you'll need to pay a fee next time, before leaving the ranch.
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"Obtained 2x＜Mana Shackles＞.","水色"
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"【Go to town】→【Town Hall】enabled.","水色"
PRINTL You can now read the 「List of Ningen who have entered the Demon Realm」
PRINTL Every day after the Midday settlement, the ningen available for tracking will be displayed,
PRINTL and you can make capture requests from the【Town Hall】.


;スレイ以外の奴隷を【屈服】状態にする
@MILESTONE_CHECK_811

FOR TARGET_COUNT,1,CHARANUM
	TARGET = TARGET_COUNT
	
	;スレイちゃんは捕獲日マイナスなので弾く
	SIF CFLAG:捕獲日 > 0 && ＃陥落状態／屈服以上＃
		RETURN 1
NEXT


;システム【部屋割り変更】解放・＜裁縫道具セット＞入手
@MILESTONE_REWARD_811

ITEM:裁縫道具セット += 1
PRINTL When Mr. Mano came to collect the goods, he admires how obedient the rebellious slave has become.
PRINTL It would be good to have more staff.
PRINTL He suggests that, if you want to treat her as an <employee>, you should give her a room.
PRINTL Maybe you could have the slave help with farm work.
PRINTL He also gave you a ＜Sewing Kit＞, in case that you are bothered by torn clothes.
PRINTL He told you to buy the ＜Mending Cloth＞ yourself at the Home Center.
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"Obtained ＜Sewing Kit＞","水色"
PRINTL 【Visit Slave】→【Fix Torn Clothes】allows you to repair worn clothes.（Requires ＜Mending Cloth＞）
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"【Management】→【Room Assignment】enabled.","水色"


;【調合知識】所持した奴隷を屈服
@MILESTONE_CHECK_812

FOR TARGET_COUNT,1,CHARANUM
	TARGET = TARGET_COUNT
	SIF CFLAG:捕獲日 > 0 && ＃陥落状態／屈服以上＃ && TALENT:調合知識
		RETURN 1
NEXT


;スケジュール【調剤】解放
@MILESTONE_REWARD_812

PRINTL A slave with mixing knowledge from the surface has surrendeded to you.
PRINTL When you mention it to Eugene, he brings you a surplus Demon World Pharmacology Basics book.
PRINTL It looks like you can make some drugs with the equipment currently on the ranch.
PRINTL You could make your slave mix the drugs.
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"【Schedule】→【Mix Drugs】enabled.","水色"



;掃除Lv5以上の奴隷を屈服
@MILESTONE_CHECK_813

FOR TARGET_COUNT,1,CHARANUM
	TARGET = TARGET_COUNT
	SIF CFLAG:捕獲日 > 0 && ＃陥落状態／屈服以上＃ && ABL:掃除 >= 5
		RETURN 1
NEXT


;システム【掃除当番変更】解放
@MILESTONE_REWARD_813

PRINTL You have a submitted slave with general cleaning knowledge.
PRINTL So far, the two of you had been cleaning, but it might be a good idea to leave the cleaning to other slaves.
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"【Management】→【Cleaning Duty】enabled.","水色"



;あなた・スレイの他に5匹の奴隷を牧場に迎える
@MILESTONE_CHECK_814

SLAVE_COUNT = 0
FOR TARGET_COUNT,1,CHARANUM
	TARGET = TARGET_COUNT
	SIF !CFLAG:追跡対象
		SLAVE_COUNT ++
NEXT

;スレイちゃん含めると6人
SIF SLAVE_COUNT >= 6
	RETURN 1


;施設【不動産】解放
@MILESTONE_REWARD_814

PRINTL The number of slaves on the ranch is increasing. It might be a good idea to add more living space.
PRINTL If you want to order something in Okachi City, it would be best to ask Makai Construction through Fudou's real estate agency.
PRINTL It is expensive, but income from milk shipments is increasing more than expected, so you can think about it.
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"【Go to town】→【Real Estate】enabled.","水色"



;奴隷3人を【恋慕】にする
@MILESTONE_CHECK_815

SLAVE_COUNT = 0
FOR TARGET_COUNT,1,CHARANUM
	TARGET = TARGET_COUNT
	SIF ＃陥落状態／恋慕以上＃
		SLAVE_COUNT ++
NEXT
SIF SLAVE_COUNT >= 3
	RETURN 1


;＜スタイリング道具セット＞入手
@MILESTONE_REWARD_815

ITEM:スタイリング道具セット += 1
PRINTL The slaves are becoming obedient and even feeling love for you. This is a good trend.
PRINTL According to Mano, "Even though she's a ningen, she's still a girl, so you should take care of her hair."
PRINTL Even though you are given the tools, you never did anything with other people's hair,
PRINTL but you feel like you could manage it, because it came with a strangely thick instruction manual?
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"Obtained ＜Styling Toolkit＞.","水色"
PRINTL You can now change your slave's hairstyle with【Visit Slave】→【Change Hairstyle】.（Changing hair color requires ＜Hair Dye＞）



;奴隷を【乳牛堕ち】させる
@MILESTONE_CHECK_816

FOR TARGET_COUNT,1,CHARANUM
	TARGET = TARGET_COUNT
	SIF CFLAG:乳牛
		RETURN 1
NEXT


;＜工具セット＞入手
@MILESTONE_REWARD_816

ITEM:工具セット += 1
PRINTL The slave fell to the pleasure of milking and declared herself a 「Dairy Cow」. You did a great job.
PRINTL Thinking about whether there were any device appropriate for the cute 「Dairy Cow」,
PRINTL you suddenly remembered that you had a set of tools in the warehouse.
PRINTL Your grandfather occasionally used it to make tools for each of the Makai Dairy Cows.
PRINTL Maybe you should try making something yourself.
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"Obtained ＜Tool Set＞.","水色"
PRINTL You can now make high-quality milking machines.【Development and Acquisition】→【Milker Development】



;奴隷を【隷属】させる
@MILESTONE_CHECK_817

FOR TARGET_COUNT,1,CHARANUM
	TARGET = TARGET_COUNT
	SIF ＃陥落状態／隷属＃
		RETURN 1
NEXT


;【強くてニューゲーム】開放
@MILESTONE_REWARD_817

PRINTL The slave became completely submissive and declared herself your 「Love Slave」.
PRINTL ...From somewhere you heard a voice saying, 「Even if you go to the next world, you'll do well」.
PRINTL What does that mean?
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"【New Game+】enabled.","水色"
PRINTL You can start it by selecting【Options】→【New Game+】.
PRINTL It is recommended to create a backup save before this.






